---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Copyright & Use of Content"
  description="Copyright information and permitted use of reports, analysis and all content produced by Michael Mulhern Football Consultancy."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Copyright & Use of Content</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal">
        <p class="legal__intro">
          &copy; Michael Mulhern, 2026. All rights reserved.
        </p>
        <p>
          Everything I create — including reports, written content, football
          analysis, development ideas, templates, frameworks, diagrams and all
          website material — is protected by copyright. This means it belongs to
          me, and you are allowed to use it, but you cannot copy it or share it
          without permission.
        </p>

        <h2>How You Can Use My Work</h2>
        <p>If you book a service or receive a report, you are welcome to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Read it</li>
          <li>Use it for your own learning and development</li>
          <li>Discuss it privately with your coach or programme</li>
          <li>Refer to it as part of your personal football journey</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This is exactly what the service is designed for.</p>

        <h2>What You Cannot Do</h2>
        <p>You must not:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Copy, share or forward my reports to others</li>
          <li>Publish or upload my content online</li>
          <li>Reuse my written work as your own</li>
          <li>Use my templates to create your own reports</li>
          <li>Reproduce my material across teams, programmes or organisations</li>
          <li>Use my work for staff training, handbooks or teaching resources</li>
        </ul>
        <p>unless you have written permission from me.</p>

        <h2>For Schools, Academies & Universities</h2>
        <p>
          Institutions may only use reports and materials for the specific player
          or team the work was created for.
        </p>
        <p>You must not:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Reuse my report format or methodology internally</li>
          <li>Adapt my templates for other players</li>
          <li>Add my content into your curriculum, coaching materials or documents</li>
          <li>Present my work as part of your own system</li>
        </ul>
        <p>unless an agreement has been made in writing.</p>

        <h2>Ownership of Methodology</h2>
        <p>
          My analysis style, structure, frameworks, development ideas and
          approach are my intellectual property. Buying a service does not
          transfer ownership of these methods.
        </p>

        <h2>If You Need Permission</h2>
        <p>
          If you wish to reuse or reference any part of my work for wider
          teaching, staff training or programme development, please
          <a href="/contact/">contact me</a> to request permission.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 2rem;
    background-color: var(--color-off-white);
  }

  .legal {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .legal__intro {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-grey-600);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .legal h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal p {
    color: var(--color-grey-600);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal a {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .legal a:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold-hover);
  }

  .legal ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .legal li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
    color: var(--color-grey-600);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .legal li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-gold);
  }
</style>
